00:17:55.480 --> 00:17:55.920
Whoa.

00:17:56.080 --> 00:17:57.720
It's twenty tokens, you know.

00:17:59.440 --> 00:18:00.560
Alright, let's hit it.

00:18:02.280 --> 00:18:07.080
♪Birthday but with me♪

00:18:07.080 --> 00:18:10.400
♪It always happens to me every single time♪

00:18:10.400 --> 00:18:13.800
♪Is this how it feels? Huh? Is that right?♪

00:18:14.200 --> 00:18:16.160
♪Thinking of me, aren't you?♪

00:18:16.320 --> 00:18:17.600
♪(Thinking of me, aren't you?)♪

00:18:17.600 --> 00:18:22.080
♪Birthday but with me♪

00:18:22.320 --> 00:18:25.640
♪It happens to me every single time♪

00:18:25.680 --> 00:18:29.680
♪The more it's like this, the more certain I am♪

00:18:29.920 --> 00:18:32.040
♪Mm, that's right♪

00:18:34.920 --> 00:18:39.000
♪(That's right, that's right)♪

00:18:39.040 --> 00:18:43.000
♪The more it's like this, the more certain I am♪

00:18:43.240 --> 00:18:45.120
♪Mm, that's right♪

00:18:53.520 --> 00:18:56.120
- Here are your twenty free tokens. - P'Three, the game's over.

00:18:56.640 --> 00:18:57.760
Sir, here you go.

00:18:58.240 --> 00:18:59.000
Thank you.

00:19:00.920 --> 00:19:02.920
Whoa, twenty tokens?

00:19:03.360 --> 00:19:04.280
Yes, twenty.

00:19:04.400 --> 00:19:06.720
If you hadn't joined me, we would've only gotten ten.

00:19:08.200 --> 00:19:10.960
- The game is over. Please step down. - Oh, we can go now?

00:19:11.400 --> 00:19:12.160
Wow, twenty tokens.

00:19:12.160 --> 00:19:13.480
- Thanks. - Let's go for the claw machine.

00:19:14.720 --> 00:19:16.960
I thought you'd be too shy.

00:19:17.640 --> 00:19:18.440
I thought so, too.

00:19:18.920 --> 00:19:20.840
I was hesitant and scared at first.

00:19:21.800 --> 00:19:23.320
But now, I feel like I've unlocked something.

00:19:24.360 --> 00:19:25.400
Thank you, P'Three,

00:19:26.040 --> 00:19:28.120
For taking me out to do something this fun.

00:19:30.080 --> 00:19:32.760
Playing games with you really is a lot of fun.

00:19:33.880 --> 00:19:35.600
Then come play with me again.

00:19:37.440 --> 00:19:38.080
But...

00:19:39.400 --> 00:19:42.640
About joining B.S. Brothers, I'm not sure at all

00:19:42.840 --> 00:19:44.880
If I'll be good enough.

00:19:45.520 --> 00:19:48.040
And I'm not even sure if I'll fit in with the others.

00:19:48.520 --> 00:19:50.280
I'm just not sure about anything now.

00:19:53.200 --> 00:19:55.240
If you think you're not good enough,

00:19:55.240 --> 00:19:56.440
I'd have to disagree

00:19:56.800 --> 00:19:58.680
Because the person who beat me in that match

00:19:59.240 --> 00:20:00.760
Definitely doesn't have trash skills.

00:20:00.800 --> 00:20:02.160
I can guarantee that.

00:20:03.640 --> 00:20:06.920
As for whether you'll fit in or not...

00:20:07.760 --> 00:20:08.920
Well...

00:20:10.320 --> 00:20:12.720
If you think it's too hard,

00:20:13.120 --> 00:20:14.320
Just think of it as a game.

00:20:14.800 --> 00:20:17.120
A super tough level that you have to clear.

00:20:17.840 --> 00:20:19.440
I believe that if it's about gaming,

00:20:19.440 --> 00:20:20.840
You can definitely beat it.

00:20:21.000 --> 00:20:22.640
Just like when you got up there and danced with me.

00:20:32.160 --> 00:20:34.080
So, while we're at it,

00:20:34.680 --> 00:20:35.880
Let's make a bet.

00:20:40.680 --> 00:20:43.080
Look. If I win this plushie,

00:20:44.000 --> 00:20:45.360
You have to join B.S. Brothers.

00:20:55.600 --> 00:20:57.840
Deal. Let's bet.

00:21:03.840 --> 00:21:04.480
Come on.

00:21:07.240 --> 00:21:08.520
There it is.

00:21:08.520 --> 00:21:10.480
Whoa, whoa, whoa!

00:21:10.480 --> 00:21:10.920
Oh...

00:21:14.800 --> 00:21:16.360
I'm just showing you it's there.

00:21:19.760 --> 00:21:21.320
Is this machine rigged?

00:21:21.480 --> 00:21:23.800
It's literally stealing my money. What the hell?

00:21:23.800 --> 00:21:26.000
I thought you said games are supposed to be fun.

00:21:29.240 --> 00:21:30.760
It's a real blast.

00:21:30.880 --> 00:21:31.600
Whoa, whoa!

00:21:38.360 --> 00:21:40.400
Whoa, whoa, whoa!

00:21:48.120 --> 00:21:49.240
This is it.

00:21:49.240 --> 00:21:49.920
Hey, hey, hey!

00:21:52.080 --> 00:21:52.920
Blow on it.

00:21:56.400 --> 00:21:56.840
Go.

00:22:01.000 --> 00:22:02.760
(Game over)

00:22:10.080 --> 00:22:12.840
As promised...

00:22:14.560 --> 00:22:16.120
I won't nag you about this anymore.

00:22:24.200 --> 00:22:25.120
Wait, P'Three.

00:22:28.280 --> 00:22:29.560
I still have one token left.

00:22:47.040 --> 00:22:47.480
Come on.

00:22:59.680 --> 00:23:01.280
I really want to play on the same team as you.

00:23:03.000 --> 00:23:04.000
Come play with me.

00:23:15.320 --> 00:23:16.000
Hey, P'Three!

00:23:16.160 --> 00:23:17.080
Whoa, whoa!

00:23:17.160 --> 00:23:18.840
- Whoa, wait! - P'Three!

00:23:28.320 --> 00:23:29.440
I got it.

00:23:33.960 --> 00:23:34.520
But...

00:23:36.680 --> 00:23:38.240
I have two conditions.

00:23:38.840 --> 00:23:39.520
Sure thing.

00:23:39.560 --> 00:23:41.920
Tell me as many as you want. I'll agree to anything.

00:23:43.520 --> 00:23:44.320
First,

00:23:45.560 --> 00:23:46.920
Every time we compete,

00:23:49.360 --> 00:23:50.800
I get to wear my bear head while playing.

00:23:53.400 --> 00:23:54.360
Second,

00:23:55.080 --> 00:23:57.120
If I feel like I can't do it and want to withdraw,

00:23:57.840 --> 00:24:01.200
Please respect my decision.

00:24:02.200 --> 00:24:03.680
Of course. No problem at all.

00:24:05.600 --> 00:24:09.080
Welcome to B.S. Brothers, Derpy Kid.

00:24:39.400 --> 00:24:42.600
Ready to meet the legends of B.S. Brothers?

00:24:47.240 --> 00:24:48.520
There he is. The first one.

00:24:52.840 --> 00:24:54.560
Meet Cher, or "Laem" as everyone calls him.

00:24:54.600 --> 00:24:56.200
The Comet Mage.

00:24:56.240 --> 00:24:59.240
He plays Mage, dealing devastating burst magic damage.

00:25:00.040 --> 00:25:00.880
Next up...

00:25:00.960 --> 00:25:03.080
She's Preaw, the Lady General.

00:25:03.120 --> 00:25:04.320
She plays Carry

00:25:04.840 --> 00:25:07.960
And is the attack damage carry the team can't live without.

00:25:09.160 --> 00:25:09.880
This guy...

00:25:10.680 --> 00:25:11.280
Jack,

00:25:12.360 --> 00:25:14.280
Or the Lone Wolf.

00:25:14.400 --> 00:25:15.880
He plays as a Dark Slayer Laner

00:25:16.080 --> 00:25:18.600
Specializing in pushing and keeping the enemies on their toes.

00:25:19.520 --> 00:25:20.680
And this one right here.

00:25:24.560 --> 00:25:25.400
He's P'Toobtub,

00:25:25.440 --> 00:25:28.440
The strategist. He plans our every single move.

00:25:30.360 --> 00:25:32.680
And as for me, the King of the Jungle.

00:25:33.320 --> 00:25:34.320
A Jungler,

00:25:34.480 --> 00:25:37.440
The backline diver with insane farming that enemies fear.

00:25:39.160 --> 00:25:44.600
And here are the legends of B.S. Brothers!

00:25:54.160 --> 00:25:54.880
Hello.

00:25:55.560 --> 00:25:56.440
My name is Soh.

00:25:56.760 --> 00:25:57.840
Or...

00:25:59.440 --> 00:26:00.480
Or...

00:26:02.280 --> 00:26:04.160
It's okay, Derpy Kid. You can think of one later.

00:26:06.880 --> 00:26:07.920
You're done talking?

00:26:10.040 --> 00:26:10.840
Hey, Jack.

00:26:11.360 --> 00:26:13.400
Help me out with the cooking.

00:26:13.720 --> 00:26:14.320
Move it.

00:26:14.640 --> 00:26:15.560
Got it.

00:26:19.560 --> 00:26:20.080
Hey,

00:26:20.880 --> 00:26:21.760
Preaw.

00:26:22.480 --> 00:26:23.320
Why didn't you call for help?

00:26:23.320 --> 00:26:25.440
How can you carry all these boxes by yourself?

00:26:26.200 --> 00:26:26.920
P'Three!

00:26:28.080 --> 00:26:29.440
Are you just going to stand there doing nothing?

00:26:30.440 --> 00:26:32.920
- Come on, there are three boxes. - Watch your mouth, dude.

00:26:33.240 --> 00:26:34.920
Why did you have to say it like that?

00:26:35.320 --> 00:26:36.640
Is there anything I can help with?

00:26:39.440 --> 00:26:40.240
Nothing.

00:27:06.280 --> 00:27:07.600
Are you okay, P'Three?

00:27:12.640 --> 00:27:13.640
You derpy kid.

00:27:14.480 --> 00:27:15.560
Be more careful.

00:27:33.360 --> 00:27:36.400
(We are B.S. Brothers)

00:27:56.760 --> 00:27:57.800
I'm okay now.

00:28:00.520 --> 00:28:02.640
My friends are just silly like that.

00:28:03.560 --> 00:28:04.720
You'll get used to them before long.

00:28:07.040 --> 00:28:10.720
Is it that obvious that I'm super nervous?

00:28:12.040 --> 00:28:12.920
Crystal clear.

00:28:13.040 --> 00:28:14.720
Like it's written on your forehead.

00:28:37.080 --> 00:28:43.280
(We are B.S. Brothers)

00:29:10.040 --> 00:29:14.280
- Numb2r, Numb2r! - Numb2r, Numb2r!

00:29:14.320 --> 00:29:17.880
We're number one!

00:29:24.880 --> 00:29:25.840
Well...

00:29:26.720 --> 00:29:28.280
Look at this. What a mess.

00:29:28.440 --> 00:29:30.000
Man, who wrote this?

00:29:30.600 --> 00:29:31.680
Where's P'Three?

00:29:33.520 --> 00:29:35.520
He should be in the cafe with P'Toobtub.

00:29:38.920 --> 00:29:40.240
Just think of it as a game.

00:29:40.640 --> 00:29:42.920
A super tough level that you have to clear.

00:29:43.640 --> 00:29:45.280
I believe that if it's about gaming,

00:29:45.320 --> 00:29:46.440
You can definitely beat it.

00:29:46.800 --> 00:29:48.280
Just like when you got up there and danced with me.

00:29:53.720 --> 00:29:56.280
So how did he manage to trick you into this?

00:29:57.520 --> 00:29:58.360
He didn't.

00:29:59.280 --> 00:30:00.320
He didn't trick me.

00:30:02.440 --> 00:30:05.080
You don't have to be so polite. We're probably the same age.

00:30:05.840 --> 00:30:06.760
Right, P'Laem?

00:30:07.400 --> 00:30:09.120
Yeah, right.

00:30:09.480 --> 00:30:11.440
Being in B.S. Brothers,

00:30:11.680 --> 00:30:12.960
You just gotta chill.

00:30:13.120 --> 00:30:15.400
No need to be so polite or anything.

00:30:15.440 --> 00:30:15.880
Yeah.

00:30:15.920 --> 00:30:17.680
Just say, "Preaw, you dumbass!"

00:30:17.760 --> 00:30:19.040
- Whoa, whoa. - Just chill.

00:30:19.640 --> 00:30:22.040
- You got it, P'Cher! - Hey, what are you doing?

00:30:22.080 --> 00:30:24.480
Hey, Soh, look at this. She's a total psycho Carry.

00:30:24.520 --> 00:30:25.800
- What are you guys doing? - You want this?

00:30:25.840 --> 00:30:27.720
- Stop, you psycho Carry! - Hey, what are you doing?

00:30:27.760 --> 00:30:29.360
- You're gonna get paint everywhere. - Bring it on!

00:30:29.360 --> 00:30:30.880
- No, no, no. - Take that!

00:30:37.960 --> 00:30:38.960
Uh, Preaw did it.

00:30:39.600 --> 00:30:40.800
No, P'Laem did it.

00:30:40.800 --> 00:30:42.280
- Hey, what? I didn't. - Well, you dodged!

00:30:42.320 --> 00:30:43.280
You guys are so dead.

00:30:43.320 --> 00:30:44.920
- Hey, I'm out! - Get back here!

00:30:44.960 --> 00:30:47.920
- Wait! What? - P'Jack, I'm not with them.

00:30:47.960 --> 00:30:49.560
- No, you are. Head in the paint! - So you want this?

00:30:49.560 --> 00:30:52.280
- Grab him! Put his head in the paint! - P'Jack, I didn't do anything.

00:30:52.280 --> 00:30:55.080
- Grab him! Hey, no! - Man, you're the culprit!

00:30:55.120 --> 00:30:57.080
- Soh, move out of the way. - Hey, don't move!

00:30:57.120 --> 00:31:00.000
- This has nothing to do with you. Move. - Stay right there. No, stop!

00:31:00.840 --> 00:31:01.760
Stop it!

00:31:04.160 --> 00:31:05.040
Preaw, hey.

00:31:05.160 --> 00:31:06.600
Come on.

00:31:12.080 --> 00:31:13.000
Bring it.

00:31:13.320 --> 00:31:14.240
Come on.

00:31:39.280 --> 00:31:40.920
P'Laem, come here!

00:31:41.200 --> 00:31:42.440
Get him! Get him!

00:32:01.720 --> 00:32:03.440
Hey, you ready?

00:32:04.800 --> 00:32:07.080
What should we do with the newbie?

00:32:07.440 --> 00:32:10.040
- Let's give him a proper welcome! - Don't mess with him!

00:32:19.720 --> 00:32:20.880
Stop messing with him.

00:32:26.680 --> 00:32:28.120
Oh, you think this is funny?

00:32:28.160 --> 00:32:30.120
- You're getting it, then. - Hey, P'Three!

00:32:31.360 --> 00:32:33.640
Laughing, huh? You think it's funny?

00:32:33.840 --> 00:32:35.400
Jeez, what are you guys even doing?

00:32:37.200 --> 00:32:39.240
Why the hell are you splashing me?

00:32:39.240 --> 00:32:41.200
P'Jack, come here! P'Laem, P'Jack!

00:32:41.320 --> 00:32:42.360
- Take this. - Hey, what?

00:33:19.800 --> 00:33:20.800
We're a mess.

00:33:21.760 --> 00:33:25.000
P'Toobtub really worked me to the bone.

00:33:25.240 --> 00:33:27.880
He kept me painting that wall. Forget about gaming.

00:33:30.360 --> 00:33:32.880
Well, well.

00:33:34.280 --> 00:33:36.000
I'm curious to see what P'Three's boy's got.

00:33:38.640 --> 00:33:39.800
Think you're pretty hot stuff, huh?

00:33:42.600 --> 00:33:44.520
Come on, let's play a couple of games.

00:33:44.560 --> 00:33:46.000
- Come on. - Yeah, okay.

00:33:46.040 --> 00:33:47.280
- Let's do it. - 05...

00:33:47.320 --> 00:33:48.480
805?

00:33:48.640 --> 00:33:50.800
- 884. - 805...

00:33:50.840 --> 00:33:52.520
- 884 - 80588...

00:33:54.000 --> 00:33:55.000
884.

00:33:55.320 --> 00:33:56.480
Let's pick our heroes.

00:34:02.720 --> 00:34:03.640
Let's go. Let's go!

00:34:07.800 --> 00:34:09.840
Whoa, you guys actually know what you're doing.

00:34:11.800 --> 00:34:13.480
Of course. We're pros at this.

00:34:13.720 --> 00:34:14.680
Do your job, Jungler.

00:34:15.080 --> 00:34:17.440
(Abyssal Dragon has been defeated)

00:34:20.800 --> 00:34:22.520
Soh, where are you going? You're on the wrong side.

00:34:25.760 --> 00:34:27.160
I'm on my way.

00:34:27.640 --> 00:34:30.160
Support, you're not tanking any damage. Faster.

00:34:32.080 --> 00:34:33.520
I'm being dove!

00:34:38.480 --> 00:34:39.560
I can't hold them off anymore.

00:34:42.440 --> 00:34:43.520
The inner turret!

00:34:44.720 --> 00:34:46.480
(The Blue Team's tower has been destroyed)

00:34:46.960 --> 00:34:47.920
They've got Blade of Eternity.

00:34:48.000 --> 00:34:49.160
Ugh, I can't do this anymore.

00:34:54.800 --> 00:34:56.200
We lost in the league, and now this...

00:34:57.160 --> 00:34:59.160
Man, I'm starving. Let's go grab some food.

00:35:00.920 --> 00:35:03.680
I'm heading home. Catch you later.

00:35:03.920 --> 00:35:05.320
I'm beat today.

00:35:05.920 --> 00:35:08.520
Exactly. He made me paint so much I'm getting jacked.

00:35:08.520 --> 00:35:10.160
Look at this. Look.

00:35:10.200 --> 00:35:11.600
- I'm out. Noodles sound good. - What?

00:35:11.600 --> 00:35:12.680
Thought we'd play a couple of games.

00:35:12.720 --> 00:35:14.840
The noodle lady won't wait forever. Noodles!

00:35:14.920 --> 00:35:17.760
I was just getting started.

00:35:18.040 --> 00:35:19.520
- What is wrong with you guys? - Catch you later, P'Three!

00:35:19.600 --> 00:35:21.640
I'm so hungry.

00:35:42.280 --> 00:35:43.520
So this is the newbie?

00:35:44.280 --> 00:35:45.880
I don't see what the hype is all about.

00:35:46.560 --> 00:35:47.120
Yeah.

00:35:48.560 --> 00:35:50.400
Three, is the kid you brought

00:35:50.440 --> 00:35:51.640
Really up for this?

00:35:52.760 --> 00:35:55.000
Come on, give him some time.

00:35:55.000 --> 00:35:56.000
I'll take care of him.

00:35:56.680 --> 00:35:57.640
Make sure you do.

00:36:11.440 --> 00:36:13.800
What? Feeling down already?

00:36:14.480 --> 00:36:15.960
You scared me, P'Three.

00:36:18.240 --> 00:36:19.880
How did you know...

00:36:20.000 --> 00:36:21.240
Because you're Derpy Kid.

00:36:25.520 --> 00:36:26.680
You're not exactly subtle.

00:36:34.840 --> 00:36:36.040
Don't stress about it. Let's go.

00:36:36.360 --> 00:36:38.560
I'll drop you at the train station when we're done tonight, okay?

00:36:39.360 --> 00:36:40.400
Okay?

00:36:54.520 --> 00:36:56.200
- P'Three... - Yeah?

00:36:56.560 --> 00:36:59.840
Actually, you don't have to drop me off.

00:36:59.920 --> 00:37:01.400
I can make my own way back.

00:37:03.240 --> 00:37:04.840
What? Who said I'm dropping you off?

00:37:05.200 --> 00:37:05.840
I'm...

00:37:07.160 --> 00:37:09.280
Just going to pick some things up.

00:37:10.120 --> 00:37:10.680
Yeah.

00:37:14.800 --> 00:37:16.080
Look at you.

00:37:16.440 --> 00:37:17.680
I'm kidding.

00:37:17.680 --> 00:37:19.120
Of course I'm dropping you off.

00:37:19.360 --> 00:37:20.520
Since you're so down like this,

00:37:20.560 --> 00:37:22.360
How could I let you go home alone?

00:37:26.080 --> 00:37:28.480
P'Three, do you remember what I told you?

00:37:29.560 --> 00:37:32.560
I said if I can't handle it, I'd ask to withdraw, remember?

00:37:35.400 --> 00:37:37.200
I remember your conditions.

00:37:39.120 --> 00:37:41.680
I don't think I'm cut out for the Pro League.

00:37:51.680 --> 00:37:52.320
But...

00:37:54.280 --> 00:37:57.760
Even if you haven't clicked with the team yet,

00:37:57.800 --> 00:37:59.840
You seem to be opening up more.

00:38:00.280 --> 00:38:01.840
That alone is a big achievement.

00:38:02.320 --> 00:38:03.920
Any better and you'd have to be me.

00:38:17.440 --> 00:38:20.320
I'd just hate for you to give up now.

00:38:20.640 --> 00:38:22.400
If you still want to keep fighting,

00:38:22.480 --> 00:38:25.160
I want to help you unlock your own achievements, too.

00:38:31.600 --> 00:38:33.520
Let's clear this level together, Soh.

00:38:43.280 --> 00:38:44.880
(Why are you tagging us right now?)

00:38:45.080 --> 00:38:48.600
Hey, I need your help with something.

00:38:49.920 --> 00:38:51.600
(You're a Pro League player, Soh.)

00:38:51.720 --> 00:38:53.600
(What do you want us to help you with?)

00:38:54.120 --> 00:38:55.680
Help me practice RoV.

00:38:58.040 --> 00:38:59.440
Watch out for the ambush in the Jungle.

00:38:59.720 --> 00:39:00.720
Hold them off.

00:39:01.680 --> 00:39:02.920
Take the tower. Now.

00:39:03.120 --> 00:39:04.640
Nice work up top. Push it. Push.

00:39:08.800 --> 00:39:09.920
They lost their inner tower.

00:39:10.000 --> 00:39:11.720
Looks like they're setting up a gank.

00:39:11.760 --> 00:39:13.400
Three of them in the bottom lane.

00:39:13.400 --> 00:39:16.720
(Dare to rematch, you bullsh*tters?)

00:39:16.760 --> 00:39:20.200
(Newbie, big mouth, trash, noob)

00:39:25.120 --> 00:39:26.880
Who the hell did this?

00:39:30.760 --> 00:39:31.920
Just wait until I find out

00:39:32.160 --> 00:39:34.040
Which little brat is behind this.

00:39:35.760 --> 00:39:38.360
Is it those backseat gamers who have beef with you, Laem?

00:39:38.520 --> 00:39:40.480
You do love pwning those brats.

00:39:41.280 --> 00:39:42.880
I don't think so.

00:39:54.960 --> 00:39:57.960
(Newbie)

00:40:02.400 --> 00:40:03.760
Don't read those things.

00:40:06.840 --> 00:40:08.040
Just look at me.

00:40:21.720 --> 00:40:24.040
Look, they even left their tag on the wall.

00:40:28.480 --> 00:40:29.280
Jeez!

00:40:29.560 --> 00:40:31.440
Should we call the cops on them?

00:40:31.720 --> 00:40:34.320
No need. Those backseat gamers are pathetic.

00:40:35.160 --> 00:40:36.760
Yeah, I'm with P'Toobtub on this.

00:40:37.120 --> 00:40:38.680
This doesn't need the police.

00:40:40.880 --> 00:40:43.120
Three, where are you going?

00:40:44.200 --> 00:40:45.200
Isn't it obvious?

00:40:46.280 --> 00:40:47.280
I'm going to...

00:40:49.480 --> 00:40:51.720
Deal with them myself. Damn it!

00:40:52.080 --> 00:40:54.680
- Let's go, Laem. Come with me. - Let's go, yeah. Let's do it.

00:40:55.560 --> 00:40:57.560
- Why would you bring that chair? - Well...

00:40:57.880 --> 00:40:58.880
- Go! - Come on.

00:40:59.480 --> 00:41:01.560
- Give me the key. - Alright, move it.

00:41:01.960 --> 00:41:02.880
Wait up!

00:41:03.520 --> 00:41:05.480
Kids, why the hell did you do that?

00:41:07.720 --> 00:41:10.240
I'm an only child of my parents, not your kid.

00:41:11.120 --> 00:41:13.240
Don't blame us for teaching you a lesson, then.

00:41:13.280 --> 00:41:14.800
Don't go crying to your dad about it, either.

00:41:14.840 --> 00:41:16.720
Is that what you did all the time when you were a kid?

00:41:16.800 --> 00:41:18.160
Is that why you think we'd do the same?

00:41:19.400 --> 00:41:21.640
You've got guts, Pod, challenging a Pro League team.

00:41:21.680 --> 00:41:23.080
I don't care how good you are

00:41:23.200 --> 00:41:25.120
As long as you have such dead weight on your team.

00:41:31.040 --> 00:41:32.480
That's what you think, too, isn't it?

00:41:32.760 --> 00:41:34.040
You just haven't said it out loud.

00:41:34.160 --> 00:41:35.040
Go on, say it.

00:41:35.040 --> 00:41:35.960
Exactly.

00:41:38.960 --> 00:41:39.840
What are you talking about?

00:41:40.680 --> 00:41:42.000
Nobody's thinking anything like that.

00:41:44.520 --> 00:41:46.240
Yeah, right now,

00:41:46.400 --> 00:41:48.400
Our team might not have quite gelled yet...

00:41:48.640 --> 00:41:51.280
But when it comes to crushing toxic brats like you,

00:41:51.640 --> 00:41:53.640
It'll be a total piece of cake.

00:41:55.720 --> 00:41:56.560
We'll see about that.

00:41:56.640 --> 00:41:59.080
How about this? Let's do a best-of-five.

00:42:02.640 --> 00:42:04.080
And if we win...

00:42:04.240 --> 00:42:05.960
You have to repaint P'Toobtub's cafe

00:42:06.000 --> 00:42:07.280
And make it look as good as new.

00:42:08.600 --> 00:42:10.000
And apologize to us, too.

00:42:10.360 --> 00:42:11.680
- Deal? - Fine.

00:42:11.720 --> 00:42:12.960
But if we win,

00:42:13.200 --> 00:42:14.280
You have to leave the team

00:42:14.520 --> 00:42:16.360
And let us join B.S. Brothers instead.

00:42:16.680 --> 00:42:17.360
Is that a deal?

00:42:23.840 --> 00:42:24.480
Deal?

00:42:24.920 --> 00:42:25.520
Deal.

00:42:27.640 --> 00:42:30.320
- Let's show them what we've got. - Yeah, bring it on.

00:42:30.840 --> 00:42:33.840
(The Blue Team's tower has been destroyed)

00:42:36.680 --> 00:42:37.400
(Infinite Slayer has been defeated)

00:42:37.440 --> 00:42:38.920
Sh*t, it's an ambush.

00:42:46.080 --> 00:42:46.520
(The Red Team's tower has been destroyed)

00:42:47.440 --> 00:42:49.000
Keep pushing. Push it.

00:42:50.440 --> 00:42:51.800
- Nice! - Nice.

00:42:51.840 --> 00:42:53.240
(Infinite Slayer has been summoned) (Vanguard is advancing)

00:42:55.000 --> 00:42:55.880
- Wrap it up! - They're dead.

00:42:55.920 --> 00:42:57.040
(The Red Team's tower has been destroyed)

00:42:57.680 --> 00:42:59.040
- Alright. - Hey, hey, hey!

00:43:07.920 --> 00:43:10.680
You're f*cking legendary, my Derya MK12.

00:43:13.120 --> 00:43:14.240
Hey, hey, hey!

00:43:16.360 --> 00:43:17.960
Keep your end of the deal, Pod.

00:43:22.600 --> 00:43:23.440
I'm sorry.

00:43:24.400 --> 00:43:27.120
What? I didn't catch that. Say it again.

00:43:27.640 --> 00:43:28.800
I said I'm sorry.

00:43:28.800 --> 00:43:30.160
What more do you want, P'Laem?

00:43:31.360 --> 00:43:33.120
You shouldn't just be apologizing to me.

00:43:34.240 --> 00:43:35.720
You need to apologize to everyone

00:43:35.760 --> 00:43:37.640
For tagging P'Toobtub's wall like that.

00:43:38.000 --> 00:43:41.000
Do you have any idea how exhausting it was to paint that?

00:43:44.320 --> 00:43:45.280
I'm sorry.

00:43:45.280 --> 00:43:47.640
I'm sorry, P'Toobtub, for tagging the wall.

00:43:47.640 --> 00:43:48.280
And...

00:43:48.400 --> 00:43:50.760
I'm sorry for looking down on you, P'Soh.

00:43:51.160 --> 00:43:52.680
It was an honest mistake.

00:43:52.880 --> 00:43:54.000
That excuse again.

00:43:56.280 --> 00:43:57.800
I'll forgive you guys,

00:43:58.160 --> 00:44:00.120
But don't you go doing this to anyone else.

00:44:00.400 --> 00:44:02.320
They would've called the cops on you.

00:44:02.400 --> 00:44:05.240
- Come on, we already said we're sorry. - We're sorry.

00:44:05.480 --> 00:44:06.280
I didn't mean any harm.

00:44:06.280 --> 00:44:08.040
We practiced so hard

00:44:08.040 --> 00:44:09.320
For that audition, though.

00:44:09.400 --> 00:44:10.720
You never got back to us

00:44:10.720 --> 00:44:13.160
After you said you'd call, right?

00:44:13.200 --> 00:44:15.560
- Yeah. - Then you just went and picked P'Soh.

00:44:15.760 --> 00:44:17.400
But he is legit good, man.

00:44:17.440 --> 00:44:18.720
Yeah, he is.

00:44:19.000 --> 00:44:20.560
Sh*t, you guys play like trash.

00:44:20.680 --> 00:44:22.560
Look, you are just kids.

00:44:22.960 --> 00:44:24.160
If you want my advice,

00:44:24.160 --> 00:44:26.480
You can be subs for B.S. Brothers for now.

00:44:26.880 --> 00:44:28.800
And if you improve, I'll let you play in the big leagues.

00:44:30.880 --> 00:44:31.880
- Really? - For real?

00:44:31.920 --> 00:44:33.400
- You mean it? - Thank you so much.

00:44:33.600 --> 00:44:34.560
Thank you.

00:44:35.680 --> 00:44:36.520
Yeah, yeah.

00:44:36.560 --> 00:44:38.200
- We're glad to be on the team. - Look forward to learning from you.

00:44:38.240 --> 00:44:39.320
Look forward to playing with you.

00:44:42.400 --> 00:44:43.720
Yeah, give it a try.

00:44:45.720 --> 00:44:46.600
Let's give them a chance.

00:44:47.320 --> 00:44:48.360
Gotta give people a chance, man.

00:44:49.600 --> 00:44:50.760
I'll give it my all.

00:44:58.840 --> 00:45:01.560
A large mookrata set is here!

00:45:01.840 --> 00:45:03.600
Look, you go serve the drinks.

00:45:03.840 --> 00:45:06.160
Hey, can someone grab a tray for the pork?

00:45:06.320 --> 00:45:07.200
I'll go get it.

00:45:07.240 --> 00:45:07.760
Alright.

00:45:09.880 --> 00:45:12.800
- Here's the extension cord. - Finally found the stove. Took me ages.

00:45:13.680 --> 00:45:15.000
It was right there in the storage.

00:45:15.040 --> 00:45:16.880
Here. Use this for the sauces.

00:45:17.840 --> 00:45:19.120
P'Toobtub, what do you want to drink?

00:45:19.360 --> 00:45:21.000
Get me some toilet water with two ice cubes.

00:45:21.040 --> 00:45:22.880
Toilet water with ice? Go drink it over there.

00:45:23.400 --> 00:45:25.480
(Dare to rematch, you bullsh*tters?)

00:45:25.480 --> 00:45:27.720
(Newbie, big mouth, trash, noob)

00:45:27.720 --> 00:45:29.600
(Only got in 'cause they were short-handed)

00:45:43.000 --> 00:45:44.040
With the weather this nice,

00:45:44.040 --> 00:45:46.120
Let's get some exercise before hitting the mookrata.

00:45:46.160 --> 00:45:47.120
Hurry up, come on.

00:45:48.720 --> 00:45:49.720
Move it.

00:45:49.720 --> 00:45:51.480
- Go on, move over. - Put it down. Put the paint down.

00:45:53.080 --> 00:45:54.080
- The paint is right here. - Hey.

00:45:54.640 --> 00:45:55.560
How can you paint all of this by yourself?

00:45:55.840 --> 00:45:57.520
- I'll cover the black paint. - We'll all help you.

00:45:58.640 --> 00:45:59.920
It's all over.

00:46:01.720 --> 00:46:02.960
Come on, don't just stand there talking.

00:46:03.000 --> 00:46:04.800
- The job won't finish itself. - You won't stop talking.

00:46:07.520 --> 00:46:08.200
Got it?

00:46:41.680 --> 00:46:42.560
You're getting the paint all over me!

00:46:42.600 --> 00:46:43.680
Sorry, sorry.

00:46:43.880 --> 00:46:45.600
Hey, newbie, refill the paint.

00:46:46.440 --> 00:46:48.080
Everyone, cheers!

00:46:50.240 --> 00:46:53.240
That was so satisfying!

00:46:53.640 --> 00:46:55.160
I know they were just some kids,

00:46:55.200 --> 00:46:57.720
But how long has it been since our team won?

00:46:57.720 --> 00:46:58.640
- Exactly. - Right.

00:46:58.640 --> 00:47:00.800
I didn't think you'd be this serious, Soh.

00:47:01.120 --> 00:47:02.640
You look all quiet and innocent,

00:47:02.960 --> 00:47:04.760
But you're an absolute beast.

00:47:04.800 --> 00:47:06.040
You're a beast.

00:47:08.680 --> 00:47:10.960
Well, you all worked so hard to finish painting the wall.

00:47:11.360 --> 00:47:13.520
If all your hard work went to waste because of me,

00:47:13.560 --> 00:47:14.920
I would have felt terrible.

00:47:15.040 --> 00:47:16.880
That's why we had to win.

00:47:18.720 --> 00:47:20.560
Soh, what shirt size do you wear?

00:47:21.480 --> 00:47:23.360
Judging by your build, you're not that big.

00:47:23.480 --> 00:47:24.600
I'll get you a team jersey.

00:47:25.560 --> 00:47:25.880
Thanks.

00:47:25.920 --> 00:47:28.800
Our team used to be just a bunch of chubby guys.

00:47:29.160 --> 00:47:29.960
- Hey. - Hey.

00:47:29.960 --> 00:47:31.200
Well, look what you feed us.

00:47:31.840 --> 00:47:32.520
Look at all this stuff.

00:47:32.520 --> 00:47:34.600
Here, Soh, I grilled this just for you.

00:47:34.600 --> 00:47:36.400
Chicken breast is good for you.

00:47:36.440 --> 00:47:37.200
Go ahead, have some.

00:47:37.240 --> 00:47:38.280
- Hey! - Hey!

00:47:38.440 --> 00:47:39.640
What's up with that?

00:47:39.840 --> 00:47:40.800
How could you do this?

00:47:40.840 --> 00:47:42.800
You used to be feeding me.

00:47:42.800 --> 00:47:44.120
Yeah, and look at you now.

00:47:44.200 --> 00:47:45.920
Man, I should file a property claim.

00:47:45.920 --> 00:47:46.440
Exactly.

00:47:46.480 --> 00:47:47.720
Because that spot next to him

00:47:47.880 --> 00:47:49.720
Used to be ours.

00:47:52.560 --> 00:47:54.160
And why are you whining, too?

00:47:58.280 --> 00:47:59.040
Guys.

00:48:01.000 --> 00:48:05.280
Actually, I have an idea for renovating P'Toobtub's cafe.

00:48:06.080 --> 00:48:07.040
I think...

00:48:07.920 --> 00:48:11.520
The cafe should have more food and lounge areas.

00:48:11.920 --> 00:48:16.040
When delivery riders come to pick up or drop off food,

00:48:16.040 --> 00:48:17.400
They'll have a place to wait.

00:48:18.040 --> 00:48:21.680
Plus, we'd attract customers who aren't just gamers.

00:48:23.000 --> 00:48:25.160
Hey, that's a great idea, Soh.

00:48:25.280 --> 00:48:25.840
I'm sold.

00:48:26.240 --> 00:48:27.280
Thanks a lot.

00:48:28.520 --> 00:48:29.920
Yeah, that's a good idea.

00:48:30.200 --> 00:48:33.000
Your cafe has been around forever. It really needs a renovation.

00:48:33.440 --> 00:48:34.360
For real.

00:48:34.520 --> 00:48:37.240
It's like your cafe's still stuck in the Numb2r era.

00:48:50.240 --> 00:48:51.200
Is it cooked yet?

00:48:51.360 --> 00:48:52.560
It's taking forever.

00:48:57.880 --> 00:48:58.760
Uh...

00:48:59.880 --> 00:49:01.080
Anyone want more pork?

00:49:58.560 --> 00:49:59.360
See ya.

00:50:00.840 --> 00:50:02.840
Hey, how are you getting home?

00:50:03.880 --> 00:50:06.000
I'm thinking of calling a ride.

00:50:06.880 --> 00:50:09.720
It's late. The Skytrain must have stopped running by now.

00:50:12.680 --> 00:50:14.280
How about you stay at my place?

00:51:12.320 --> 00:51:14.040
You still haven't been able to quit, have you?

00:51:39.200 --> 00:51:40.360
What the hell are you doing here now?

00:51:42.600 --> 00:51:43.960
I've always liked coming here.

00:51:45.160 --> 00:51:46.320
You should know that by now.

00:51:51.200 --> 00:51:52.960
Do you think I'd believe someone like you?

00:51:57.920 --> 00:51:59.640
Then why do you think I came?

00:52:00.560 --> 00:52:01.360
Because of you?

00:52:02.520 --> 00:52:03.320
Is that it?

00:52:31.840 --> 00:52:33.160
Put on the slippers.

00:52:35.080 --> 00:52:36.840
Go take a shower.

00:52:37.040 --> 00:52:38.160
You can barely keep your eyes open.

00:52:38.520 --> 00:52:39.000
Okay.

00:52:52.800 --> 00:52:54.920
There's no place to put it, so...

00:52:55.760 --> 00:52:57.080
I just tossed it on the bed for now.

00:52:59.040 --> 00:52:59.840
Thank you.

00:53:02.520 --> 00:53:06.600
You helped me unlock my achievements.

00:53:11.080 --> 00:53:14.840
Did me just standing here looking cool really help you that much?

00:53:20.360 --> 00:53:21.800
I'm really happy

00:53:23.160 --> 00:53:25.080
That you brought me into B.S. Brothers.

00:53:30.000 --> 00:53:31.640
You've worked really hard, Derpy Kid.

00:53:39.120 --> 00:53:40.280
Keep it up.

00:53:40.360 --> 00:53:42.320
This was only the first level.

00:53:47.360 --> 00:53:48.080
Want to take a shower?

00:53:48.920 --> 00:53:49.440
Yes.

00:53:54.480 --> 00:53:55.560
P'Three!

00:53:56.240 --> 00:53:57.800
I forgot to bring my clothes in.

00:53:57.840 --> 00:53:59.400
Could you grab them for me, please?

00:54:09.480 --> 00:54:11.480
P'Three, why aren't you wearing any clothes?

00:54:13.880 --> 00:54:15.280
Why are you coming in?

00:54:16.280 --> 00:54:17.440
I'm just bringing you your clothes.

00:54:18.160 --> 00:54:19.200
What kind of dirty thoughts are you having?

00:54:20.000 --> 00:54:22.080
Shouldn't you go put some clothes on first?

00:54:22.440 --> 00:54:23.600
I'm gonna do some laundry.

00:54:24.240 --> 00:54:25.120
Or do you think...

00:54:27.080 --> 00:54:28.520
I'm going to do something to you?

00:54:29.720 --> 00:54:30.200
Huh?

00:55:06.800 --> 00:55:08.400
Are you sure you're giving this to me?

00:55:09.560 --> 00:55:10.400
I am.

00:55:10.840 --> 00:55:12.680
After all, it's the first plushie you managed to win

00:55:12.680 --> 00:55:14.200
With your own hard work, isn't it?

00:55:15.960 --> 00:55:18.600
I feel like I've just unlocked an achievement.

00:55:18.880 --> 00:55:20.320
I've literally never won one before.

00:55:23.080 --> 00:55:24.160
Well, well.

00:55:25.000 --> 00:55:27.800
Did the claw machine expert from earlier already leave?

00:55:27.840 --> 00:55:30.040
Hey, watch it.

00:55:30.120 --> 00:55:31.440
You've barely joined the team,

00:55:31.480 --> 00:55:32.960
And you're already giving me attitude?

00:55:41.240 --> 00:55:43.680
Thank you, Derya MK12.

00:55:48.120 --> 00:55:49.320
Go on, get yourself home.

00:55:49.760 --> 00:55:50.720
Let me know when you're home.

00:55:52.440 --> 00:55:53.160
Got it,

00:55:53.840 --> 00:55:55.120
Mr. Thr33Gamer.

00:55:57.920 --> 00:55:59.240
- I'm leaving. - See ya.

